<div id="index">
  <div class="left-container">
    <h2>Recent Campaigns</h2>
    <div id="index_map"></div>
    <div class="jumbotron">
      <% if @campaigns %>
        <ul>
          <% @campaigns.each do |campaign| %>
            <li><table>
                  <tr>
                    <td><%= link_to campaign.name, campaign %></td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td><%= link_to campaign.leader.username, campaign.leader %></td>
                  </tr>
                  <% if campaign.location %>
                    <tr>
                      <td><%= campaign.location.address %></td>
                    </tr>
                  <% end %>
                </table>
              </li>
          <% end %>
        </ul>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="right-container">
    <h2>What is Party Quest?</h2>
      <p>Party Quest is a companion for any aspiring campaign masters out there. With it you have the option to create campaigns across the land. Would-be adventurers have the option to accompany the campaign master to tackle the chosen quests and increase their prestige.</p>
  </div>
</div>
